{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.1","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:1","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019av\u00e8nement du Seigneur<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. Jud v. 14-19. (Mt 24:37-39. 2 Th 1:7-10.) (\u00c9s 51:6. Ap 20:11.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Voici d\u00e9j\u00e0, bien-aim\u00e9s, la seconde lettre que je vous \u00e9cris. Dans l\u2019une et dans l\u2019autre je cherche \u00e0 \u00e9veiller par des avertissements votre saine intelligence,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.2","name":"2 Pierre 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.22","name":"2 Pierre 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.2","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:2","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>afin que vous vous souveniez des choses annonc\u00e9es d\u2019avance par les saints proph\u00e8tes, et du commandement du Seigneur et Sauveur, enseign\u00e9 par vos ap\u00f4tres,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.3","name":"2 Pierre 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.1","name":"2 Pierre 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.3","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:3","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>sachant avant tout que, dans les derniers jours, il viendra des moqueurs avec leurs railleries, marchant selon leurs propres convoitises,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.4","name":"2 Pierre 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.2","name":"2 Pierre 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.4","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:4","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>et disant: O\u00f9 est la promesse de son av\u00e8nement? Car, depuis que les p\u00e8res sont morts, tout demeure comme d\u00e8s le commencement de la cr\u00e9ation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.5","name":"2 Pierre 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.3","name":"2 Pierre 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.5","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:5","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ils veulent ignorer, en effet, que des cieux exist\u00e8rent autrefois par la parole de Dieu, de m\u00eame qu\u2019une terre tir\u00e9e de l\u2019eau et form\u00e9e au moyen de l\u2019eau,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.6","name":"2 Pierre 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.4","name":"2 Pierre 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.6","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:6","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>et que par ces choses le monde d\u2019alors p\u00e9rit, submerg\u00e9 par l\u2019eau,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.7","name":"2 Pierre 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.5","name":"2 Pierre 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.7","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:7","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>tandis que, par la m\u00eame parole, les cieux et la terre d\u2019\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent sont gard\u00e9s et r\u00e9serv\u00e9s pour le feu, pour le jour du jugement et de la ruine des hommes impies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.8","name":"2 Pierre 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.6","name":"2 Pierre 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.8","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:8","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Mais il est une chose, bien-aim\u00e9s, que vous ne devez pas ignorer, c\u2019est que, devant le Seigneur, un jour est comme mille ans, et mille ans sont comme un jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.9","name":"2 Pierre 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.7","name":"2 Pierre 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.9","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:9","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Le Seigneur ne tarde pas dans l\u2019accomplissement de la promesse, comme quelques-uns le croient; mais il use de patience envers vous, ne voulant pas qu\u2019aucun p\u00e9risse, mais voulant que tous arrivent \u00e0 la repentance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.10","name":"2 Pierre 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.8","name":"2 Pierre 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.10","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:10","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le jour du Seigneur viendra comme un voleur; en ce jour, les cieux passeront avec fracas, les \u00e9l\u00e9ments embras\u00e9s se dissoudront, et la terre avec les \u0153uvres qu\u2019elle renferme sera consum\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.11","name":"2 Pierre 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.9","name":"2 Pierre 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.11","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:11","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-18: cf. (Lu 21:34-36. 1 Th 5:1-10. 1 Pi 1:13-16.) (\u00c9s 65:17. Ap 21:1-5.) \u00c9p 4:14, 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Puisque donc toutes ces choses doivent se dissoudre, quelles ne doivent pas \u00eatre la saintet\u00e9 de votre conduite et votre pi\u00e9t\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.12","name":"2 Pierre 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.10","name":"2 Pierre 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.12","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:12","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>tandis que vous attendez et h\u00e2tez l\u2019av\u00e8nement du jour de Dieu, \u00e0 cause duquel les cieux enflamm\u00e9s se dissoudront et les \u00e9l\u00e9ments embras\u00e9s se fondront!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.13","name":"2 Pierre 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.11","name":"2 Pierre 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.13","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:13","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Mais nous attendons, selon sa promesse, de nouveaux cieux et une nouvelle terre, o\u00f9 la justice habitera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.14","name":"2 Pierre 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.12","name":"2 Pierre 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.14","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:14","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, bien-aim\u00e9s, en attendant ces choses, appliquez-vous \u00e0 \u00eatre trouv\u00e9s par lui sans tache et irr\u00e9pr\u00e9hensibles dans la paix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.15","name":"2 Pierre 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.13","name":"2 Pierre 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.15","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:15","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Croyez que la patience de notre Seigneur est votre salut, comme notre bien-aim\u00e9 fr\u00e8re Paul vous l\u2019a aussi \u00e9crit, selon la sagesse qui lui a \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.16","name":"2 Pierre 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.14","name":"2 Pierre 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.16","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:16","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>C\u2019est ce qu\u2019il fait dans toutes les lettres, o\u00f9 il parle de ces choses, dans lesquelles il y a des points difficiles \u00e0 comprendre, dont les personnes ignorantes et mal affermies tordent le sens, comme celui des autres \u00c9critures, pour leur propre ruine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.17","name":"2 Pierre 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.15","name":"2 Pierre 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.17","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:17","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Vous donc, bien-aim\u00e9s, qui \u00eates avertis, mettez-vous sur vos gardes, de peur qu\u2019entra\u00een\u00e9s par l\u2019\u00e9garement des impies, vous ne veniez \u00e0 d\u00e9choir de votre fermet\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.18","name":"2 Pierre 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.16","name":"2 Pierre 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.18","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 3:18","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.003.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1John.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.3.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mais croissez dans la gr\u00e2ce et dans la connaissance de notre Seigneur et Sauveur J\u00e9sus-Christ. A lui soit la gloire, maintenant et pour l\u2019\u00e9ternit\u00e9! Amen!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3","name":"2 Pierre 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1John.1.1","name":"1 Jean 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:1John.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.17","name":"2 Pierre 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbf342b33.04067256');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbf342b33.04067256\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbf342b33.04067256","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbf342b33.04067256'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbf342b33.04067256\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}